<ITEM>A Letter from Gen. Murray to Sir William Draper, dated Jan. 13.</ITEM>
<ITEM>An An&s;wer from Sir William Draper.</ITEM>
<ITEM>A Letter from Sir William Draper to Gen. Murray, dated Jan. 16.</ITEM>
